0)==========History=============================

Beta Release: 05.05.05

v0.1 : 15.11.05 



1)==========Installation instructions============

System requirements:

tested on:
    os: Linux Fedora 3, MacOS,
    compiler: gcc 3.3.3

mandatory:
    Geant4.6 or higher

optional: 
    OpenGL (Mesa), ROOT 4.x 

to compile:

   %  ./configure
   %  make


2)==========Getting Started============

to run:

    bdsim [options]

f.e. 
    bdsim --file=line.gmad --output=root

to see the full list of options:

    bdsim --help


Some input examples are available in ./examples/ directory. 
For more details documentation

3)==========Directories===================

parser/          : gmad parser
examples/        : sample lettices
docs/		 : documentation
utils/           : various "useful" scripts
